{"surah":{"number":85,"name":"البروج","englishName":"Al-Buruj","englishTranslation":"The Mansions of the Stars","ayahCount":22},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:43.743Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"By the sky containing great stars","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ","english":"By the sky","translit":"wal-samāi","root":"سمو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذَاتِ","english":"containing","translit":"dhāti","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْبُرُوجِ","english":"the constellations","translit":"l-burūji","root":"برج"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And [by] the promised Day","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْيَوْمِ","english":"And the Day","translit":"wal-yawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْعُودِ","english":"Promised","translit":"l-mawʿūdi","root":"وعد"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And [by] the witness and what is witnessed,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَشَاهِدٍۢ","english":"And (the) witness","translit":"washāhidin","root":"شهد"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَمَشْهُودٍۢ","english":"and what is witnessed","translit":"wamashhūdin","root":"شهد"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"Cursed were the companions of the trench","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قُتِلَ","english":"Destroyed were","translit":"qutila","root":"قتل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبُ","english":"(the) companions","translit":"aṣḥābu","root":"صحب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأُخْدُودِ","english":"(of) the pit","translit":"l-ukh'dūdi","root":"خدد"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"[Containing] the fire full of fuel,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","english":"(Of) the fire","translit":"al-nāri","root":"نور"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذَاتِ","english":"full","translit":"dhāti","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْوَقُودِ","english":"(of) the fuel","translit":"l-waqūdi","root":"وقد"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"When they were sitting near it","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"When","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُمْ","english":"they","translit":"hum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","english":"by it","translit":"ʿalayhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"قُعُودٌۭ","english":"(were) sitting","translit":"quʿūdun","root":"قعد"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"And they, to what they were doing against the believers, were witnesses.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","english":"And they","translit":"wahum","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"over","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَفْعَلُونَ","english":"they were doing","translit":"yafʿalūna","root":"فعل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","english":"to the believers","translit":"bil-mu'minīna","root":"أمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"شُهُودٌۭ","english":"witnesses","translit":"shuhūdun","root":"شهد"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And they resented them not except because they believed in Allah, the Exalted in Might, the Praiseworthy,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَقَمُوا۟","english":"they resented","translit":"naqamū","root":"نقم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ","english":"[of] them","translit":"min'hum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُوا۟","english":"they believed","translit":"yu'minū","root":"أمن"},{"position":7,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْعَزِيزِ","english":"the All-Mighty","translit":"l-ʿazīzi","root":"عزز"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْحَمِيدِ","english":"the Praiseworthy","translit":"l-ḥamīdi","root":"حمد"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"To whom belongs the dominion of the heavens and the earth. And Allah, over all things, is Witness.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"The One Who","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"for Him","translit":"lahu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مُلْكُ","english":"(is) the dominion","translit":"mul'ku","root":"ملك"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","english":"(of) the heavens","translit":"l-samāwāti","root":"سمو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ","english":"and the earth","translit":"wal-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"and Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/085_009_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/085_009_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/085_009_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/085_009_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"شَهِيدٌ","english":"(is) a Witness","translit":"shahīdun","root":"شهد","audio":"wbw/085_009_011.mp3"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"Indeed, those who have tortured the believing men and believing women and then have not repented will have the punishment of Hell, and they will have the punishment of the Burning Fire.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَتَنُوا۟","english":"persecuted","translit":"fatanū","root":"فتن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","english":"the believing men","translit":"l-mu'minīna","root":"أمن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُؤْمِنَـٰتِ","english":"and the believing women","translit":"wal-mu'mināti","root":"أمن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَتُوبُوا۟","english":"they repented","translit":"yatūbū","root":"توب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فَلَهُمْ","english":"then for them","translit":"falahum","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"عَذَابُ","english":"(is the) punishment","translit":"ʿadhābu","root":"عذب"},{"position":11,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ","english":"(of) Hell","translit":"jahannama","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَلَهُمْ","english":"and for them","translit":"walahum","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"عَذَابُ","english":"(is the) punishment","translit":"ʿadhābu","root":"عذب"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلْحَرِيقِ","english":"(of) the Burning Fire","translit":"l-ḥarīqi","root":"حرق"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"Indeed, those who have believed and done righteous deeds will have gardens beneath which rivers flow. That is the great attainment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believe","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَعَمِلُوا۟","english":"and do","translit":"waʿamilū","root":"عمل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ","english":"the righteous deeds","translit":"l-ṣāliḥāti","root":"صلح"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٌۭ","english":"(will be) Gardens","translit":"jannātun","root":"جنن"},{"position":8,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","english":"flow","translit":"tajrī","root":"جري"},{"position":9,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"تَحْتِهَا","english":"underneath it","translit":"taḥtihā","root":"تحت"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ ۚ","english":"the rivers","translit":"l-anhāru","root":"نهر"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/085_011_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْفَوْزُ","english":"(is) the success","translit":"l-fawzu","root":"فوز","audio":"wbw/085_011_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلْكَبِيرُ","english":"the great","translit":"l-kabīru","root":"كبر","audio":"wbw/085_011_015.mp3"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"Indeed, the vengeance of your Lord is severe.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَطْشَ","english":"(the) Grip","translit":"baṭsha","root":"بطش"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَشَدِيدٌ","english":"(is) surely strong","translit":"lashadīdun","root":"شدد"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"Indeed, it is He who originates [creation] and repeats.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed He","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"He","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يُبْدِئُ","english":"originates","translit":"yub'di-u","root":"بدأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَيُعِيدُ","english":"and repeats","translit":"wayuʿīdu","root":"عود"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And He is the Forgiving, the Affectionate,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"And He","translit":"wahuwa","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْغَفُورُ","english":"(is) the Oft-Forgiving","translit":"l-ghafūru","root":"غفر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْوَدُودُ","english":"the Most Loving","translit":"l-wadūdu","root":"ودد"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Honorable Owner of the Throne,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذُو","english":"Owner (of)","translit":"dhū","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْعَرْشِ","english":"the Throne","translit":"l-ʿarshi","root":"عرش"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمَجِيدُ","english":"the Glorious","translit":"l-majīdu","root":"مجد"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"Effecter of what He intends.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَعَّالٌۭ","english":"Doer","translit":"faʿʿālun","root":"فعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّمَا","english":"of what","translit":"limā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يُرِيدُ","english":"He intends","translit":"yurīdu","root":"رود"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"Has there reached you the story of the soldiers -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَلْ","english":"Has","translit":"hal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَتَىٰكَ","english":"come to you","translit":"atāka","root":"أتي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَدِيثُ","english":"(the) story","translit":"ḥadīthu","root":"حدث"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْجُنُودِ","english":"(of) the hosts","translit":"l-junūdi","root":"جند"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"[Those of] Pharaoh and Thamud?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِرْعَوْنَ","english":"Firaun","translit":"fir'ʿawna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَثَمُودَ","english":"and Thamud","translit":"wathamūda","root":""}]},{"number":19,"translation":"But they who disbelieve are in [persistent] denial,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَلِ","english":"Nay","translit":"bali","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"Those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieve","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(are) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَكْذِيبٍۢ","english":"denial","translit":"takdhībin","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"While Allah encompasses them from behind.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","english":"But Allah","translit":"wal-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَرَآئِهِم","english":"behind them","translit":"warāihim","root":"وري"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مُّحِيطٌۢ","english":"encompasses","translit":"muḥīṭun","root":"حوط"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"But this is an honored Qur'an","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"It","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قُرْءَانٌۭ","english":"(is) a Quran","translit":"qur'ānun","root":"قرأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَّجِيدٌۭ","english":"Glorious","translit":"majīdun","root":"مجد"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"[Inscribed] in a Preserved Slate.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فِى","english":"In","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَوْحٍۢ","english":"a Tablet","translit":"lawḥin","root":"لوح"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَّحْفُوظٍۭ","english":"Guarded","translit":"maḥfūẓin","root":"حفظ"}]}]}
